article_title: Doctors, Hospitals Brace For Larger Aetna, Anthem Or UnitedHealth

article_metadata.description: As talk of merger-mania hits the health insurance industry, doctors and hospitals worry about potential market clout of these companies if the so-called “Big 5” publicly-traded insurers dwindle to four or even three. In the past month, there have been several reports Aetna (AET) might buy Cigna (CI) or Humana (HUM). [...]
article_metadata.author: Bruce Japsen
